dmca.title: Subpoena Report
dmca.body: sbc internet service,recieved subpoena to produce the names,address,phone number,and e-mail address of subscriber whos ip addresses listed,i recieved this on 12-24-2004,sbc mailed copy to me on 12-20-2004.they were to release information to plaintiffs on 12-22-2004.how was this suppose to be prohibited if i didnt get letter until after it was already released,it says i have until 01-01-2005 to file motion to quash.how do i go about this or do i need to.i do not have any peer to peer or alleged software on pc,nor do i have any media or music on pc that would have any effect towards me.
